     1Рєњ# Deprecated Рђд
   227Рєњ## Removed Рђд
   229Рєњ### Short option flag longer than a single character
   231РєњShort option flags like `-ws` were never supported, but the old README did not make this clear. The README now states that short options are a single character.
   232Рєњ
   233Рєњ- README updated in Commander v3.
   234Рєњ- Deprecated from Commander v9.
